{"inkVersion":21,"root":[["ev","str","^Verdict","/str","str","^Neutral","/str",{"x()":"AddChar","exArgs":2},"out","/ev","\n","ev","str","^","/str",{"x()":"ChangeName","exArgs":1},"out","/ev","\n","^(The day of the trial...)","\n","^(The door swings open and in front of you is the courtroom where justice will be decided upon today.)","\n","^(A man from the defense side stands and turns towards you.)","\n","ev","str","^Grumpy Guy","/str",{"x()":"ChangeName","exArgs":1},"out","/ev","\n","ev","str","^Berg","/str","str","^Neutral","/str",{"x()":"AddChar","exArgs":2},"out","/ev","\n","^\"Hmph! I see the prosecution has finally decided to grace us with their presence.\"","\n","ev","str","ev",{"x()":"GetName"},"out","/ev","/str",{"x()":"ChangeName","exArgs":1},"out","/ev","\n","^“Good morning. Who are you?”","\n","ev","str","^Grumpy Guy","/str",{"x()":"ChangeName","exArgs":1},"out","/ev","\n","ev","str","^Berg","/str","str","^Rage","/str",{"x()":"ChangeEmote","exArgs":2},"out","/ev","\n","^“Who am I? Who are you that you think you can just show up suddenly and take over this case that I have been working diligently on for months!”","\n","ev","str","^Mr. Richards","/str",{"x()":"ChangeName","exArgs":1},"out","/ev","\n","ev","str","^Richards","/str","str","^Frown","/str",{"x()":"AddChar","exArgs":2},"out","/ev","\n","^“Mr. Berg, please treat this courtroom and my assistant with the decorum they both deserve and stop shouting.”","\n","ev","str","^Mr. Berg","/str",{"x()":"ChangeName","exArgs":1},"out","/ev","\n","ev","str","^Berg","/str","str","^Smug","/str",{"x()":"ChangeEmote","exArgs":2},"out","/ev","\n","^“Assistant, huh? I see. Getting too old to keep up, Herrmann?”","\n","ev","str","^Berg","/str",{"x()":"RemoveChar","exArgs":1},"out","/ev","\n","ev","str","^","/str",{"x()":"ChangeName","exArgs":1},"out","/ev","\n","^(Berg cracks a cheeky smile and turns back towards his desk to sit.)","\n","ev","str","^Mr. Richards","/str",{"x()":"ChangeName","exArgs":1},"out","/ev","\n","ev","str","^Richards","/str","str","^Facepalm","/str",{"x()":"ChangeEmote","exArgs":2},"out","/ev","\n","^“Ignore him, ","ev",{"x()":"GetName"},"out","/ev","^. He will do his best to get under your skin but he’s just jealous that you ended up with this case because we fired him.”","\n","ev","str","^Berg","/str","str","^Angry","/str",{"x()":"AddChar","exArgs":2},"out","/ev","\n","ev","str","^Mr. Berg","/str",{"x()":"ChangeName","exArgs":1},"out","/ev","\n","^“Unjustly fired, I might add!”","\n","ev","str","^Berg","/str",{"x()":"RemoveChar","exArgs":1},"out","/ev","\n","ev","str","^Mr. Richards","/str",{"x()":"ChangeName","exArgs":1},"out","/ev","\n","^(Mr. Richards puts his head in his palm and sighs.)","\n","^“At any rate, we should take our seats. The judge should be here soon.”","\n","ev","str","^Richards","/str",{"x()":"RemoveChar","exArgs":1},"out","/ev","\n","ev","str","^Verdict","/str",{"x()":"RemoveChar","exArgs":1},"out","/ev","\n","ev","str","^TrialScript","/str",{"x()":"SetScript","exArgs":1},"out","/ev","\n","end",["done",{"#f":5,"#n":"g-0"}],null],"done",{"#f":1}],"listDefs":{}}